    "It involves extracting aspect terms, categories, corresponding sentiment polarities, and opinion terms from dialogues.",
    "Inspired by Gao et al. (2022), these tasks can be combined flexibly like Lego bricks to form various compound tasks in Fig. 3.",
    "This Lego-style assembly provides a more flexible solution for ABSA.",
    "This review primarily focuses on ACOSQE research, as presented in Table 1.",
